summary: This document is an email chain from June 2020 between law enforcement personnel, likely from the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force, regarding the receipt of new records related to Ghislaine Maxwell, specifically Amazon and phone records. It indicates an ongoing investigation into Maxwell.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The subject of the email chain and the investigation; new Amazon and phone records related to her are being shared among law enforcement.

events.title: Transmission of Maxwell Investigation Records
events.description: Law enforcement personnel share new Amazon and phone records related to Ghislaine Maxwell via email.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain from June 2020 concerning the Ghislaine Maxwell investigation.
It shows law enforcement (NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force) actively sharing new records, specifically Amazon and phone records, related to Maxwell.
The correspondence indicates an ongoing, collaborative investigation into Maxwell by a joint task force.
